node.text:
🍣 Whenever we need our Mentaiko Fix, we will always visit @omotesingapore for it! Love their Mentaiko Salmon Belly - and they are not stingy at all with the sauce!⁣
⁣
They also offer a variety of chirashi bowls, sushi and mains for takeaways and delivery! Save time by ordering in advance! Collection at counter or drive thru. Check out their ig @omotesingapore for more deets!⁣
⁣
